}}</ref>\n|23||5||2||3||colspan=2|\u2014||11{{efn|Four appearances and two goals in UEFA Champions League, seven appearances and one goal in UEFA Europa League}}||3||1{{efn|name=statsM}}||1||37||12\n|-\n|[[2019 Rosenborg BK season|2019]]<ref name=Soccerway/>\n|5||0||0||0||colspan=2|\u2014||0||0||0||0||5||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!57||24||4||3||colspan=2|\u2014||23||7||2||1||86||35\n|-\n|rowspan=2|[[F.C. Copenhagen|Copenhagen]]\n|[[2019\u201320 Danish Superliga|2019\u201320]]\n|rowspan=1|[[Danish Superliga]]\n|6||0||1||1||colspan=2|\u2014||1{{efn|name=UEL}}||0||colspan=2|\u2014||8||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!6||0||1||1||colspan=2|\u2014||1||0||colspan=2|\u2014||8||1\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!298||72||27||10||23||9||68||20||3||2||418||113\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n===International===\n{{updated|match played 27 March 2018}}<ref name=ATeamstats/>\n\n{|class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n|+ [[Denmark national football team|Denmark]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n!scope=row|2006\n|4||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2007\n|10||3\n|-\n!scope=row|2008\n|8||3\n|-\n!scope=row|2009\n|9||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2010\n|4||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2011\n|10||5\n|-\n!scope=row|2012\n|10||5\n|-\n!scope=row|2013\n|2||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2014\n|7||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2015\n|10||3\n|-\n!scope=row|2016\n|0||0\n|-\n!scope=row|2017\n|5||1\n|-\n!scope=row|2018\n|2||0\n|-\n!scope=row|Total\n!81!!30\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''As of match played 27 March 2018. Denmark score listed first, score column indicates score after each Bendtner goal.''<ref name=ATeamstats>{{cite web |url=https://www.dbu.dk/landshold/landsholdsdatabasen/PlayerInfo/5111&teamtypeid=330#match |title=Nicklas Bendtner: A-Landshold (Alle kampe) |language=Danish |trans-title=A-internationals (all matches) |publisher=Dansk Boldspil-Union |accessdate=26 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ International goals scored by Nicklas Bendtner\n|-\n! scope=col | {{abbr|No.|Cumulative goals total}}\n! scope=col | Cap\n! scope=col 