center | 45\n| 15 November 2011 || [[Blue Water Arena]], [[Esbjerg]], Denmark || {{fb|FIN}}\n| style=text-align:center | 2\u20131\n| style=text-align:center | 2\u20131 || Friendly\n|-\n! scope=row | 18\n| style=text-align:center | 47\n| 26 May 2012 || [[Imtech Arena]], [[Hamburg]], Germany || {{fb|BRA}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20133\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20133 ||Friendly\n|-\n! scope=row | 19\n| rowspan=2 style=text-align:center | 50\n| rowspan=2 | 13 June 2012\n| rowspan=2 | [[Arena Lviv]], [[Lviv]], Ukraine\n| rowspan=2 | {{fb|POR}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20132\n| rowspan=2 style=text-align:center | 2\u20133\n| rowspan=2 | [[UEFA Euro 2012 Group B|UEFA Euro 2012]]\n|-\n! scope=row | 20\n| style=text-align:center | 2\u20132\n|-\n! scope=row | 21\n| style=text-align:center | 53\n| 12 October 2012 || [[Vasil Levski National Stadium]], [[Sofia]], Bulgaria || {{fb|BUL}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20131\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20131 || [[2014 FIFA World Cup qualification \u2013 UEFA Group B|2014 FIFA World Cup qualification]]\n|-\n! scope=row | 22\n| style=text-align:center | 55\n| 14 November 2012 || [[T\u00fcrk Telekom Arena]], [[Istanbul]], Turkey || {{fb|TUR}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20130\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20131 || Friendly\n|-\n! scope=row | 23\n| rowspan=2 style=text-align:center | 56\n| rowspan=2 | 11 October 2013\n| rowspan=2 | Parken Stadium, Copenhagen, Denmark\n| rowspan=2 | {{fb|ITA}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20131\n| rowspan=2 style=text-align:center | 2\u20132 \n| rowspan=2 | 2014 FIFA World Cup qualification\n|-\n! scope=row | 24\n| style=text-align:center | 2\u20131\n|-\n! scope=row | 25\n| rowspan=2 style=text-align:center | 63\n| rowspan=2 | 14 November 2014\n| rowspan=2 | [[Partizan Stadium]], [[Belgrade]], Serbia\n| rowspan=2 | {{fb|SRB}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20131\n| rowspan=2 style=text-align:center | 3\u20131 \n| rowspan=2 | [[UEFA Euro 2016 qualification]]\n|-\n! sco