anish Football Player of the Year#Young Players of the Year|Danish Under-17 Player of the Year]]: 2004<ref name=U17PotY/>\n*Danish Talent of the Year: 2007<ref name=AretsTalent>{{cite web |url=https://spillerforeningen.dk/projekter/spillernes-officielle-k%C3%A5ringer/%C3%A5rets-talent/ |title=\u00c5rets Talent |language=Danish |trans-title=Talent of the year |publisher=Spillerforeningen (Danish Professional Footballers' Association) |accessdate=14 April 2017 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229031047/https://spillerforeningen.dk/projekter/spillernes-officielle-k%C3%A5ringer/%C3%A5rets-talent/ |archivedate=29 December 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Danish Football Player of the Year]]: 2009<ref name=PotY2009/>\n*Danish Goal of the Year: 2009<ref name=PotY2009/>\n*[[List of Eliteserien top scorers|Eliteserien top scorer]]: [[2017 Eliteserien|2017]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://mobil.bold.dk/fodbold/nyheder/bendtner-tog-topscorertitlen-i-debutsaeson/ |title=Bendtner tog topscorertitlen i debuts\u00e6son |language=Danish |trans-title=Bendtner took the top scorer title in his debut season |first=Kenneth |last=Hansen |website=Bold.dk |date=26 November 2017 |accessdate=26 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20140619194909/http://www.arsenal.com/first-team/players/nicklas-bendtner Player profile] at Arsenal F.C. website\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Denmark squads\n| bg = #e11b22\n| fg = white\n| list1 = \n{{Denmark squad 2010 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Denmark squad UEFA Euro 2012}}\n}}\n{{Eliteserien top scorers}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bendtner, Nicklas}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen]]\n[[Category:Danish footballers]]\n[[Category:Denmark youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Denmark under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Denmark international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association foot