onal football team|Denmark]]\n|-\n!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n!scope=row|2006\n|4||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2007\n|10||3\n|-\n!scope=row|2008\n|8||3\n|-\n!scope=row|2009\n|9||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2010\n|4||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2011\n|10||5\n|-\n!scope=row|2012\n|10||5\n|-\n!scope=row|2013\n|2||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2014\n|7||2\n|-\n!scope=row|2015\n|10||3\n|-\n!scope=row|2016\n|0||0\n|-\n!scope=row|2017\n|5||1\n|-\n!scope=row|2018\n|2||0\n|-\n!scope=row|Total\n!81!!30\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n:''As of match played 27 March 2018. Denmark score listed first, score column indicates score after each Bendtner goal.''<ref name=ATeamstats>{{cite web |url=https://www.dbu.dk/landshold/landsholdsdatabasen/PlayerInfo/5111&teamtypeid=330#match |title=Nicklas Bendtner: A-Landshold (Alle kampe) |language=Danish |trans-title=A-internationals (all matches) |publisher=Dansk Boldspil-Union |accessdate=26 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ International goals scored by Nicklas Bendtner\n|-\n! scope=col | {{abbr|No.|Cumulative goals total}}\n! scope=col | Cap\n! scope=col | Date\n! scope=col | Venue\n! scope=col | Opponent\n! scope=col | Score\n! scope=col | Result\n! scope=col | Competition\n|-\n! scope=row | 1\n| style=text-align:center | 1\n| 16 August 2006 || [[Odense Stadium]], [[Odense]], Denmark || {{fb|POL}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20130\n| style=text-align:center | 2\u20130 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|-\n! scope=row | 2\n| style=text-align:center | 2\n| 1 September 2006 || [[Br\u00f8ndby Stadion]], [[Br\u00f8ndbyvester]], Denmark || {{fb|POR}}\n| style=text-align:center | 4\u20132\n| style=text-align:center | 4\u20132 || Friendly\n|-\n! scope=row | 3\n| style=text-align:center | 6\n| 28 March 2007 || [[MSV-Arena]], [[Duisburg]], Germany || {{fb|GER}}\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20130\n| style=text-align:center | 1\u20130 || Friendly\n|-\n! scope=row | 4\n| style=text-align:center | 13\n| 17 November 2007 || [[Windsor Park]], [[Belfast]], Northern 